24:51.825 --> 24:55.203
♫ Leave your guns
at home, Bill ♫

24:55.287 --> 25:00.667
♫ Don't take your guns to town ♫

25:00.750 --> 25:02.043
To the man in black.

25:05.005 --> 25:07.174
Love this fucking song.

25:11.720 --> 25:13.555
What?
The shooting pain?

25:13.638 --> 25:16.266
Shrapnel,
finding its way out.

25:16.349 --> 25:18.935
Why don't you
just get this removed?

25:19.019 --> 25:21.980
Well, doctor says my choice.

25:22.063 --> 25:24.357
I hate hospitals anyway.

25:24.441 --> 25:25.775
Maybe you like pain.

25:27.319 --> 25:31.031
Sometimes things
become part of you.

25:31.114 --> 25:32.657
Whether you like it or not.

25:38.872 --> 25:42.751
What is this?
Is this a picture of baby?

25:42.834 --> 25:47.339
My grandson gets
baptized tomorrow morning.

25:47.422 --> 25:49.174
I don't think
I'm going to make it.

25:49.257 --> 25:50.926
I haven't even met the kid yet.

25:51.009 --> 25:53.720
Yeah, but, you know,
he sent this invitation,

25:53.803 --> 25:55.388
I'm sure
he wants you to go.

25:55.472 --> 25:58.725
Well, my wife,
well, my ex-wife,

25:58.808 --> 26:02.312
she's going to bring her
new- hell, I say new,

26:02.395 --> 26:06.274
but she's been married,
what, going on 20 years now.

26:06.358 --> 26:09.945
And you know the kicker? Kicker?
What's "kicker?"

26:10.028 --> 26:12.072
Suprise.
Surprise, yes.

26:12.155 --> 26:16.159
The new guy, he was
best man at our wedding.

26:16.243 --> 26:20.163
Oh, mother fucker.
You're kidding.

26:20.247 --> 26:21.998
Yup.

26:22.082 --> 26:23.833
He's all right.
He ain't a bad guy.

26:23.917 --> 26:26.753
He's been there for my son.

26:26.836 --> 26:29.506
He's been actually more
of a father than I have.

26:29.589 --> 26:34.552
I've been, you know,
away and here and there.

26:34.636 --> 26:36.137
You know, just...

26:38.056 --> 26:40.850
<i>Oh, come on, Ben.</i>

26:40.934 --> 26:45.939
Let me read something for you.
You test my German. Okay.

26:46.022 --> 26:49.401
<i>It is the hunter's honor
that he protects</i>

26:49.484 --> 26:53.530
and preserves his game,
hunts sportsmanlike,

26:53.613 --> 26:58.368
and honors the creator
and his creatures.

27:01.663 --> 27:06.501
Benjamin, did you honor
the creator in him?

27:06.584 --> 27:08.878
I didn't kill him.
You didn't?

27:08.962 --> 27:12.048
I haven't killed anything in 20 years.
You're joking.

27:12.173 --> 27:16.428
No. Everything you see here inside, outside, all bullshit.
Bullshit, what do you mean-

27:16.511 --> 27:18.179
Everything here,
bullshit car,

27:18.263 --> 27:20.974
bullshit house,
bullshit fiberglass bow,

27:21.057 --> 27:24.853
bullshit heads on a wall, it's all bullshit.
Come on, I would love to have this.

27:24.936 --> 27:26.896
Want to hear
something pathetic?

27:26.980 --> 27:29.649
This was all here when I bought this place.
You're joking.

27:29.733 --> 27:33.903
No. Furnished with rustic interior
design elements. Oh, my God.

27:33.987 --> 27:38.325
That's what the listing said. That's it. It's all bullshit.
That is not the man you are.

27:38.408 --> 27:41.244
I mean I grew up in a place
like this, but not as big

27:41.328 --> 27:44.164
and actually not as fancy,
but it was, you know,

27:44.247 --> 27:48.585
it was the real deal, mountains,
trees, hung out with my dad.

27:48.668 --> 27:51.796
Hey, I'll show you something.
You'll get a kick out of this.

27:58.470 --> 27:59.929
That was my dad's.
What is this?

28:00.013 --> 28:03.016
Silver star
for gallantry in action.

28:03.099 --> 28:06.436
But does he have some war
stories to tell, huh? Oh, yeah.

28:06.519 --> 28:09.439
I fought three different wars,
four different countries,

28:09.522 --> 28:11.441
still couldn't get
one of these.

28:11.524 --> 28:12.984
Really?

28:13.068 --> 28:17.364
No prize for Ben.
That's not good.

28:17.447 --> 28:20.617
All the good things you did,
you know, why not-

28:20.700 --> 28:23.411
I remember the first time
we went hunting,

28:23.495 --> 28:25.497
I told him
I wanted to use his bow.

28:25.580 --> 28:29.209
